Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,op
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.04,0:00:10.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快上啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.97,0:00:11.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,动作快点
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.69,0:00:29.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胜负已分 到此为止
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.47,0:00:35.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 接下来还有斗士要挑战她吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.34,0:00:40.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,参加费是金币一枚 赢了就能拿金币二十枚
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.15,0:00:41.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 没人上吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.80,0:00:43.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老子可是花了钱看你们打的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.94,0:00:44.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来挑战
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.52,0:00:49.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多谢惠顾
